review_blob: Absolutely love this beer. Tasty hops, smooth flavor, and easy to drink. Easily one of the best beers out. Too bad you can pretty much only find it at the brewery
Not a porter guy but this was decent. Could really taste the caramel undertones. Would drink again
Definitely one if my favorite non-San Diego ipa?s. More flavor than bitter, but can taste the dry hops
Nice aftertaste. Not very bitter, but high abv for a brunette and very easy to drink.
